<indexterm zone="gimp-pixel-rgn-get-rect"><primary sortas="gimp_pixel_rgn_get_rect">gimp_pixel_rgn_get_rect</primary></indexterm><programlisting><link linkend="void">void</link>                gimp_pixel_rgn_get_rect             (<link linkend="GimpPixelRgn">GimpPixelRgn</link> *pr,
